app_description: About: You can draw everything what you want on blank paper use the painter brush tools and make it to one picture save it and share with it. You can edit your photos apply effects add stickers remove blemishes whiten smiles and so much more! It Includes: Pen Line Arrow Rect Stroke Rect Fill Ellipse Stroke Ellipse Fill Eraser Text Text Multiline Effects Focus Frames Stickers Enhance Orientation Crop Lighting Color Splash Text Redeye Whiten Blemish Many many colors tools filters and effects and they are all FREE!. Features: Enhance with Hi Def Scenery Food Portrait and Night Stylize with over 100 free and purchasable filters Get creative with stunning stickers frames and overlays Touch up selfies with redeye and blemish removal Boost smile wattage with teeth whitening Selectively remove and replace color with Splash Add drama with Sharpness Add text and create your own memes Crop rotate and straighten your photos Draw attention to the subject of your photo with Focus or Vignette Modify brightness contrast highlights and shadows Adjust saturation warmth tint and fade Share photos to TikTok Instagram Facebook X Print your favorite photos to the nearest Walgreens
